Direct Known Subclasses:
Entity, Raw.Compound, Raw.EscapedLiteral
public class Raw
extends AbstractSequenceableAlternative

Base class for expressions that are readily combined with other similar expressions. This encompasses special predefined expressions, processed literals, and combinations thereof. This class mainly exists so that long sequences of such expressions can be flattened rather than causing the construction of deep trees.
